### Pattern A — `items.map()`

**Mode:** Run Once for All Items *(default)*
**Returns:** an array of items

```js
return $input.all().map(item => ({
  json: { ...item.json, /* ... */ }
}));
```

Use when you're thinking in batches: bulk transforms, dedup, fan-in, fan-out.

